data.description: Check out this contemporary home that is centrally located in Ruidoso!  Near the corner of Hull Rd and Gavilan Rd, sits this amazing low maintenance site built home built in 2004 that is ready to begin some great mountain memories within. This home boasts a stucco exterior, half circle driveway, oversized 2 car garage, central AC/Heat, fenced back yard, storage shed, wood burning fireplace, bonus room off living area, and connected to city utilities.  It is also a one level home on a level lot so you won't have to struggle with stairs.  The home sits on a large lot with no other homes located on the left side of it currently.  Ample parking for guests make it suitable for entertaining as well.  Home is being sold unfurnished, but some furniture is negotiable.  Don't miss out on this one!
